{"tid":1323823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果721係對政府重力一擊就要去金鐘/中環","createTime":"2019-07-16T11:20:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T15:29:48.000Z","uid":224095,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"93071ad88fab306f8f393a128adf25760b7b755c","tid":1323823,"uid":224095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:20:07.000Z","msg":"金鐘警犬玩就玩到熟哂，但如果去非金鐘/中環呢啲地方根本同之前光復行動冇分別。<br />\n<br />\n針對唔到政權/香港經濟命脈，只會影響到民生，到時手足想做野又一大班和理非走出黎話留力又剩。<br />\n<br />\n巷戰銅鑼灣個格局同旺角差唔多，而家唔係起革命打差佬打巷戰冇意思，甚至會分散示威者，警察亦容易包圍剿滅示威者。<br />\n<br />\n甚至如果警察改變策略保持克制，等到凌晨先出擊。到時示威者又白費一日。<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇"},{"pid":"b2738bd50c5f0c64517c013573420cd8246769a6","tid":1323823,"uid":224095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:21:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0d37ba3491c6ac6c67a8984883ae1f21263e6eaa","tid":1323823,"uid":224095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:22:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"253b257a169f9d6f187a1a64af0880038c36fe51","tid":1323823,"uid":29218,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:22:42.000Z","msg":"西環如何"},{"pid":"b248dbd31b62506d4969bf16abe14f70fb16c760","tid":1323823,"uid":224095,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:25:30.000Z","msg":"去銅鑼灣，警察唔出擊又係on99一日。<br />\n<br />\n前幾次搞到咁大係因為警察主動撩事鬥非。<br />\n<br />\n但今次警察明知人數將會係七月以黎最大規模，有機會變陣"},{"pid":"99e7d73990e2d40a2bbd62a66e36da2533127414","tid":1323823,"uid":224095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:28:39.000Z","msg":"見到有post講宣傳。<br />\n<br />\n屌你咩仲宣傳乜撚野。而家要對準政權，又去幫中國爭取民主？走左廿年直到五年大家都知條路行唔通，而家竟然去走回頭路？"},{"pid":"0f882d786204b9797d3583f3476bb9dcf0304ccc","tid":1323823,"uid":224095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:28:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"275a0e8a65f03fdaece2c686a8054ab6157d6932","tid":1323823,"uid":224095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:30:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5fd33802a0d038daab7cc08e5c7cb1a8bc92c95f","tid":1323823,"uid":224095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:44:24.000Z","msg":"星期日今次係1/7後香港人召集，向政府重申五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n而家去銅鑼灣輸出革命做乜9<br />\n<br />\n銅鑼灣係令自己處於被動角色等警察出擊。如果警察唔理，好似以往9/6，16/6咁克制，示威者係銅鑼灣係冇乜作為。"},{"pid":"94420b68a140033cbce20c69407de0bb990414ac","tid":1323823,"uid":224095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:44:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b4c2ebbaf3d48a40a5a231a8a2d4afd1b5ec0d8e","tid":1323823,"uid":224095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:45:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e3eb59181804e2b1c32e3b75f10fae893b2c890b","tid":1323823,"uid":11049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:46:20.000Z","msg":"點解唔係起革命？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40aac4a9441d88f92fe2ab619b9c4edf8cbca6f3","tid":1323823,"uid":224095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3eb59181804e2b1c32e3b75f10fae893b2c890b","tid":1323823,"uid":11049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:46:20.000Z","msg":"點解唔係起革命？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:47:54.000Z","msg":"香港人真係夠膽打？<br />\n<br />\n上次唔係有狗落單都唔會比人狂打"},{"pid":"4b6d79f86b0952e9a7b5f5d5a15ae646bcb7288a","tid":1323823,"uid":276355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:48:27.000Z","msg":"去銅鑼灣"},{"pid":"f1705085ec75a9c3498fafe9f40575fb2d3e19e2","tid":1323823,"uid":224095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b6d79f86b0952e9a7b5f5d5a15ae646bcb7288a","tid":1323823,"uid":276355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:48:27.000Z","msg":"去銅鑼灣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:49:37.000Z","msg":"銅鑼灣搞光復有咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a03ef1cba86d942528d88555b6ae87f5cb43a104","tid":1323823,"uid":224095,"like":0,"d